Maintainer: Nick McKay <nick@nau.edu>
Description: Plotting and mapping for LiPD (Linked Paleo Data) datasets and
    time-uncertain ensemble analyses, including age model ensembles,
    timeseries ribbons and stacks, correlation, regression, spectral, and
    PCA results, and site maps. Split out of the 'geoChronR' package.
